@startuml poc_state
title OpenSDLC PoC — PipelineState 상태 다이어그램

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  BorderColor #2980B9
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  StartColor #2C3E50
  EndColor #2C3E50
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}

[*] --> Booting : python run_poc.py 실행

state Booting {
  : config.py 임포트 (load_dotenv)
  : 경로/프로바이더/모델 설정
  : API 키 검증
  : pipeline YAML 파싱
}

Booting --> GraphBuilding : API 키 유효

Booting --> [*] : API 키 없음\n(exit 1)

state GraphBuilding {
  : lru_cache로 AgentConfig 전부 로드
  : 각 step → node_fn 클로저 생성
  : system_prompt 조립 (8단계)
  : 엣지 연결 (단순 / 조건부)
  : graph.compile()
}

GraphBuilding --> Running : compiled.invoke(initial_state)

state Running {

  state Requirements {
    state "ReqAgent 실행중" as req {
      : user_story → LLM 호출
      : UseCaseModelArtifact 생성
    }
    state "ValidatorAgent 실행중\n(UC 검증)" as val_uc {
      : UC artifact만 입력 (context 격리)
      : _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE 적용
      : ValidationReportArtifact 생성
    }
    req --> val_uc
  }

  state RoutingUC <<choice>>
  Requirements --> RoutingUC : validation_result 확인

  RoutingUC --> TestDesign : pass
  RoutingUC --> Requirements : warning/fail\n(iteration_count < max)
  note on link #FFE0E0
    iteration_count++
    _build_user_message() 재작업 모드:
    이전 UC + fail 사유 포함
  end note
  RoutingUC --> MaxRetriesExceeded : warning/fail\n(iteration_count >= max)

  state TestDesign {
    state "TestAgent 실행중\n(mode=design)" as ta_design {
      : UC artifact → TestDesignArtifact
    }
    state "ValidatorAgent 실행중\n(TD 검증)" as val_td {
      : TestDesign artifact 검증
    }
    ta_design --> val_td
  }

  state RoutingTD <<choice>>
  TestDesign --> RoutingTD

  RoutingTD --> Implementation : pass
  RoutingTD --> TestDesign : warning/fail (재작업)
  RoutingTD --> MaxRetriesExceeded : 한계 초과

  state Implementation {
    state "CodeAgent 실행중" as code {
      : UC + TestDesign → ImplementationArtifact
      : _CODE_FILE_MANDATE 적용
      : code_files 포함 (완전한 실행 코드)
    }
    state "ValidatorAgent 실행중\n(Impl 검증)" as val_impl {
      : Impl artifact 검증
    }
    code --> val_impl
  }

  state RoutingImpl <<choice>>
  Implementation --> RoutingImpl

  RoutingImpl --> TestExecution : pass
  RoutingImpl --> Implementation : warning/fail (재작업)
  RoutingImpl --> MaxRetriesExceeded : 한계 초과

  state TestExecution {
    state "TestAgent 실행중\n(mode=execution)" as ta_exec {
      : TestDesign + Impl → TestReportArtifact
    }
    state "ValidatorAgent 실행중\n(TR 검증)" as val_tr {
      : TestReport artifact 검증
    }
    ta_exec --> val_tr
  }

  state RoutingTR <<choice>>
  TestExecution --> RoutingTR

  RoutingTR --> Feedback : pass
  RoutingTR --> TestExecution : warning/fail (재작업)
  RoutingTR --> MaxRetriesExceeded : 한계 초과

  state Feedback {
    state "CoordAgent 실행중" as coord {
      : TestReport → FeedbackArtifact
    }
  }
}

Running --> Saving : Feedback 완료

state Saving {
  : steps_completed → iteration별 그룹화
  : output/iteration-N/artifacts/*.yaml 저장
  : ImplementationArtifact → code_files 추출
  : output/workspace/ 에 실행 코드 저장
  : pipeline_status = "completed"
}

state MaxRetriesExceeded {
  : pipeline_status = "max_retries_exceeded"
  : iteration_count >= max_iterations 도달
}

state QuotaExhausted {
  : QuotaExhaustedError 발생
  : pipeline_status = "quota_exhausted"
  : partial artifacts 저장 가능
  note
    daily quota 소진 시
    (not transient rate limit)
    지금까지 생성된 artifacts는
    _save_artifacts()로 저장 가능
  end note
}

Running --> QuotaExhausted : QuotaExhaustedError\n(LLM daily quota 소진)

Saving --> [*] : 정상 완료
MaxRetriesExceeded --> [*] : 비정상 종료 (exit 2)
QuotaExhausted --> [*] : 중단 종료

note right of Running
  **validation_result 3가지 값**:
  - "pass"    → 다음 Phase 진행
  - "warning" → fail과 동일 처리 (rework)
  - "fail"    → rework or max_retries

  **iteration_count**:
  ValidatorAgent가 warning/fail 판정 시
  +1 증가.
  max_iterations (기본 3) 초과 시 강제 종료.
end note

note right of GraphBuilding
  **lru_cache 동작**:
  load_all_agents()는 최초 1회만
  *.config.yaml을 읽고,
  이후 호출은 캐시 반환.
  process 재시작 전까지 유효.
end note

note bottom of Saving
  **artifact 파일명 규칙**:
  {local_seq:03d}_{artifact_id}.yaml
  예: 001_UC-01.yaml
      002_UC-01-VAL-1.yaml
      003_IMPL-01.yaml
end note

@enduml
